A Process Hazard Analysis must be performed on each of the covered processes using a team with the appropriate expertise;
The Hazard Analysis method may be HAZOP, FMEA, WHAT-IF, CHECKLIST, or an equivalent method appropriate to the complexity of the process;
The hazard analysis must address:
